{"title":"Japan Reopens Borders to Foreign Nationals","link":"https://iafor.org/japan-reopens-borders-to-foreign-nationals/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=japan-reopens-borders-to-foreign-nationals","date":1646876743000,"content":"<p><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Japan-Reopens-Borders-to-Foreign-Nationals-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Japan Reopens Borders to Foreign Nationals\" srcset=\"https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Japan-Reopens-Borders-to-Foreign-Nationals-150x150.jpg 150w, https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Japan-Reopens-Borders-to-Foreign-Nationals-600x600.jpg 600w, https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Japan-Reopens-Borders-to-Foreign-Nationals-100x100.jpg 100w, https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Japan-Reopens-Borders-to-Foreign-Nationals-50x50.jpg 50w, https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Japan-Reopens-Borders-to-Foreign-Nationals-300x300.jpg 300w, https://iafor.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Japan-Reopens-Borders-to-Foreign-Nationals-32x32.jpg 32w\" />After almost two full years of closed borders, on Tuesday, March 1, 2022, the Government of Japan eased entry restrictions and is now accepting applications for foreign nationals to enter the country, including business travellers and those attending academic conferences. IAFOR will work with the Japanese health ministry to facilitate the entry of conference presenters <a href=\"https://iafor.org/japan-reopens-borders-to-foreign-nationals/\">...</a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://iafor.org/japan-reopens-borders-to-foreign-nationals/\">Japan Reopens Borders to Foreign Nationals</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://iafor.org\">The International Academic Forum (IAFOR)</a>.</p>","author":"IAFOR","siteTitle":"The International Academic Forum (IAFOR)","siteHash":"db6175d8277e1d8dd86d5cc607b1dd9335cce255aa7e00b46d0931f23a0d47f6","entryHash":"dde0c4e7235a496c85367c0d1f29c9a931d838119b8a8b5684b340f9a408928f"